      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_5f9c4ab08cac7457e9111a30e4664920607ea2c115a1433d7be98e97e64244ca.pdf_2_15",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "The index was designed specifically for the agricultural community to assist in evaluating potential water quality impacts from farming operations. It builds on established indices that exam- ine instream conditions and incorporates a series of measurements that evaluate land use impacts on water quality. It also assists producers in evaluating the suc-",
        "bbox": [
          0.637984496124031,
